    "title": "新たな価値観のインストール",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "今日のトレーニングを確認していると、\r\nミホノブルボンに声をかけられた。",
            "enText": "As I was checking my training for the day, I \nwas approached by Michonobourbon.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "pathId": -804961697984364210,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "失礼いたします。\r\n問題解決に向け、助言を頂けないでしょうか。",
            "enText": "Please excuse me. I would like to ask for \nyour advice on how to solve my problem.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -1023512404761545414
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -7847055391845962339
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -964626138960816595,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "以前のサイボーグ疑惑事件では、\r\nあなたの助力により事態が収束しました。",
            "enText": "The previous cyborg scandal was \nresolved with your help.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 4733014894077079986
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -6498569683867008909
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 3814556352263003787
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1069952848033742085,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "以来、問題解決能力が高いと認識しており、\r\n現在、声をかけさせていただいています。",
            "enText": "Since then, we have recognised that you are \na good problem solver, and we are now \ncalling on you.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -1061277017492108236
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 1481577024787490909
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1383639189606022500,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "問題とは、サイボーグ疑惑解決以降、\r\n『走り』についての質問が増えたことです。",
            "enText": "The problem is that since the resolution of \nthe cyborg scandal, there have been more \nquestions about \"running\".",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 6577726161076972662
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 2705832714922499851
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1361647660835880548,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "先日は、同室のニシノフラワーさんより、\r\nより速く直線を走る方法を問われました。",
            "enText": "The other day I was asked by my roommate, \nNishino Flower, how to run faster \nin a straight line.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -3863193563033697608
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 7980427295667295719
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4524708924391344821,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "経験より仮説を打ち出し、\r\n答えを提示したのですが――",
            "enText": "I put forward a hypothesis based on my \nexperience, and I provided an answer.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 771178748189908670
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 5527276962388937349
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3013625934514816333,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ニシノフラワー",
            "enName": "Nishino Flower",
            "jpText": "私、ミホノブルボンさんみたいに、\r\nカッコよく直線を走りきりたいんです！",
            "enText": "I want to run down the straight \nlike Mihono Bourbon!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 9163106147869639597
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 9059733198889899522
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -3357812071462114381
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -87072961226557036
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -3598848921356196030
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -3445780471210002443
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2030297690478966575,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "直線の走行については、前後方向のみに\r\n力が発生するよう意識しています。",
            "enText": "In a straight line, we are conscious of the \nfact that the force is generated only in the \nforward and backward directions.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -9095913644220766474
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 5189087176307401399
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": -5707363494503112989
