            "pathId": -8768615703306095913,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "これらの経験値から、私では力不足であり、\r\n彼女への関わりは非合理的だと判断しました。",
            "enText": "Based on these experiences, I decided that I \nwas not strong enough and that my \ninvolvement with her was irrational.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -7459961519469553430
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 3033693948214650697
                }
