            "pathId": -4536116345912592185,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミホノブルボン",
            "enName": "Mihono Bourbon",
            "jpText": "プロが一言教示した方が効率的です。\r\n彼女を指導してもらえないでしょうか。",
            "enText": "It is more efficient for a professional \nto teach you a few words. Would you \nbe willing to mentor her?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 3192569224149157446
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -4803261903134710572
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7899719971598194237,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……彼女の話から、\r\nひとつ気になることがあった。",
            "enText": "… There was one thing that \nstruck me from her story.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 77,
